---
---
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-inner container">

    <!-- Full-width headline above the grid -->
    <h1 class="hero-headline anim anim-d2">
      Breaking down how financial institutions and the world's most successful businesses are built — the strategy, the customer behavior, and <em>why some win.</em>
    </h1>

    <!-- Two-column grid below -->
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <!-- Left column -->
      <div class="hero-left">
        <p class="hero-sub anim anim-d3">
          From bank earnings and payments strategy to the business models behind the world's most successful companies — connecting strategy, customer behavior, and the decisions that separate winners from everyone else.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-throughline anim anim-d3">
          Most fintech problems aren't technical. They're behavioral.
        </div>
        <div class="hero-tags-block anim anim-d4">
          <p class="hero-tags-label">What we cover:</p>
          <ul class="hero-tags">
            <li>Banking Earnings &amp; Strategy</li>
            <li>Money Movement &amp; Payments</li>
            <li>Consumer Behavior</li>
            <li>Platforms &amp; Product Strategy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-ctas anim anim-d5">
          <a href="#research-posts" class="btn-primary">View Research</a>
          <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost">About RP3</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: featured card -->
      <div class="hero-right anim anim-d4">
        <p class="hero-featured-label">Latest:</p>
        <a href="/research/q1-2026-banking-earnings" class="hero-card">
          <div class="hero-card-meta">
            <span class="hero-card-category">Research</span>
            <span class="hero-card-dot">·</span>
            <span class="hero-card-date">April 2026</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="hero-card-title">Q1 2026 Banking Earnings: What the Numbers Are Really Saying</h3>
          <p class="hero-card-excerpt">JPMorgan set the tone. Wells Fargo is still transitioning. Capital One completed the Discover acquisition. Ally is the one to watch — and hasn't reported yet.</p>
          <ul class="hero-card-tags">
            <li>Banking</li>
            <li>Earnings</li>
            <li>Q1 2026</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="hero-card-read">Read <span class="hero-card-arrow">→</span></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="hero-ambient" aria-hidden="true">R</div>
</section>
<style>
  .hero { position:relative; min-height:100svh; display:flex; align-items:center; overflow:hidden; padding-top:var(--nav-h); }
  .hero::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E"); background-size:200px; pointer-events:none; opacity:0.5; }
  .hero-inner { position:relative; z-index:1; padding-top:clamp(32px,6vw,80px); padding-bottom:clamp(64px,10vw,120px); }

  /* Full-width headline */
  .hero-headline { font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:clamp(30px,3.6vw,52px); font-weight:300; line-height:1.12; letter-spacing:-0.02em; color:var(--ink); max-width:92%; margin-bottom:clamp(28px,3vw,44px); }
  .hero-headline em { font-style:italic; color:var(--accent); }

  /* Two-column grid */
  .hero-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr; gap:clamp(40px,6vw,96px); align-items:start; }

  /* Left column */
  .hero-sub { font-size:clamp(15px,1.6vw,18px); line-height:1.75; color:var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom:28px; font-weight:300; }
  .hero-throughline { font-size:14px; line-height:1.65; color:var(--ink-muted); font-weight:300; letter-spacing:0.01em; font-style:italic; border-left:2px solid #C49A3C; padding-left:16px; margin-bottom:36px; }
  .hero-tags-block { margin-bottom:36px; }
  .hero-tags-label { font-family:var(--font-body); font-size:11px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom:12px; }
  .hero-tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; }
  .hero-tags li { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); border:1px solid var(--rule); padding:6px 14px; border-radius:2px; font-weight:400; }
  .hero-ctas { display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .btn-primary { display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper); font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:500; border-radius:2px; transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.2s; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background:#2a2a2a; transform:translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-ghost { display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; border:1px solid rgba(14,14,14,0.25); color:var(--ink-muted); font-size:13px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:400; border-radius:2px; transition:border-color 0.2s,color 0.2s; }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color:var(--ink); color:var(--ink); }

  /* Right column — featured card */
  .hero-right { position:relative; z-index:1; padding-top:clamp(12px,2vw,28px); }
  .hero-featured-label { font-family:var(--font-body); font-size:11px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom:14px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
  .hero-featured-label::before { content:''; display:block; width:20px; height:1px; background:var(--accent); }
  .hero-card { display:block; border:1px solid var(--rule); border-top:3px solid var(--accent); background:var(--paper-warm); padding:28px; border-radius:2px; transition:box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .hero-card:hover { box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(14,14,14,0.08); transform:translateY(-2px); }
  .hero-card-meta { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .hero-card-category { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); font-weight:500; }
  .hero-card-dot { color:var(--ink-faint); font-size:12px; }
  .hero-card-date { font-size:11px; color:var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing:0.06em; }
  .hero-card-title { font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:clamp(18px,1.8vw,24px); font-weight:400; color:var(--ink); line-height:1.25; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .hero-card-excerpt { font-size:13px; line-height:1.75; color:var(--ink-muted); font-weight:300; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .hero-card-tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .hero-card-tags li { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-faint); border:1px solid var(--rule); padding:3px 9px; border-radius:2px; font-weight:400; }
  .hero-card-read { font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-muted); display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; transition:color 0.2s; }
  .hero-card:hover .hero-card-read { color:var(--ink); }
  .hero-card-arrow { transition:transform 0.25s; }
  .hero-card:hover .hero-card-arrow { transform:translateX(4px); color:var(--accent); }

  /* Ambient letter */
  .hero-ambient { position:absolute; right:-0.05em; bottom:-0.15em; font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:clamp(280px,40vw,680px); font-weight:300; line-height:1; color:transparent; -webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(14,14,14,0.06); pointer-events:none; user-select:none; z-index:0; }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width:768px) {
    .hero-headline { max-width:100%; }
    .hero-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:48px; }
    .hero-ambient { display:none; }
    .hero-inner { padding-block:60px 72px; }
  }
</style>
